_I hope this letter finds you in good health. It's been a long time since we last met, and I miss you more than you can imagine. The days seem emptier without you, and there are so many things I would like to tell you in person._

_I would like to invite you to come to Milan. I have some important matters we need to discuss, and I think it's time we met face to face._

_With much love,_
_Dad_

